gram\": \"the title\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the 17-year-old's achievement unfolded in the waters of Marseille Marina, the journey started three years ago in Paris, the host city of the 2024 Games.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.6748721061074373, \"rank\": 0.48176223457806105, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}, {\"begin\": 750, \"end\": 755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999968604243, \"rank\": 3.139389055672326e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 17-year-old's achievement\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the waters\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 689}, {\"ngram\": \"the journey\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"the host city\", \"from\": 757, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Games\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a media interview alongside Maximilian on Aug 14 at the People's Association headquarters, Minister for Culture, Community and Youth Edwin Tong revealed how he first learnt of the teenager's talent in 2021 through a former law school classmate, who happened to be Maximilian's aunt.\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 822, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999983290554473, \"rank\": 1.6452721951960851e-06, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999983290554473, \"rank\": 1.6452721951960851e-06, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a media interview\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 839}, {\"ngram\": \"the People's Association headquarters\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"Culture\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"the teenager's talent\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"a former law school classmate\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had told him during a meeting in the French capital, \\\"My nephew is a champion kitefoiler\\\", prompting him to take notice.\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1119, \"end\": 1125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.999780580492663, \"rank\": 0.00013524479702192748, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a meeting\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"My nephew\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1145}, {\"ngram\": \"a champion kitefoiler\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"notice\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She told me about him... and that I should meet with him... and it struck a chord,\\\" said Mr Tong.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"score\": 0.9999977509676508, \"rank\": 2.249037367919682e-06, \"text\": \"Tong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"