d said, 'Can I meet with Max and his mum?'\\\"\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1623, \"end\": 1626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cavalera\", \"score\": 0.9873654760075857, \"rank\": 0.00930751844091986, \"text\": \"Max\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cavalera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Max_Cavalera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a call\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1571}, {\"ngram\": \"my classmate\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"his mum\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not often that a 14-year-old leaves an indelible mark on a minister, but that was exactly what Maximilian did at that very first meeting in 2021 at Mr Tong's office.\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999983290554473, \"rank\": 1.6452721951960851e-06, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 1800, \"end\": 1804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"score\": 0.9999977509676508, \"rank\": 2.249037367919682e-06, \"text\": \"Tong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an indelible mark\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"a minister\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1743}, {\"ngram\": \"that very first meeting\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1785}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The homeschooled teenager's maturity and keen grasp of mathematical concepts, and how they relate to the wind, \\\"blew me away\\\", Mr Tong recalled.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1946, \"end\": 1950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"score\": 0.9999977509676508, \"rank\": 2.249037367919682e-06, \"text\": \"Tong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The homeschooled teenager's maturity\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"keen grasp\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1867}, {\"ngram\": \"mathematical concepts\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"the wind\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1925}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He was such a measured young boy, very mature, spoke about his sport in a very convincing way,\\\" said the sports minister.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such a measured young boy\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1995}, {\"ngram\": \"his sport\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"a very convincing way\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2056}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports minister\", \"from\": 2064, \"to\": 2083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think if you remember, you told me about trigonometry and wind direction,\\\" he said to Maximilian, to which the teenager quipped: \\\"I mean, you asked a technical question.\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2175, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999983290554473, \"rank\": 1.6452721951960851e-06, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"trigonometry\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"wind direction\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"the teenager\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"a technical question\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not help myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2284, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Work then started on finding a winning formula.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Work\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"a winning formula\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Tong looked at how Maximilian could be supported in both sporting and financial ways, paving the way for him to be competitive on the world stage in men's kitefoil.\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"score\": 0.9999977509676508, \"rank\": 2.249037367919682e-06, \"text\": \"Tong\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pete_Tong\"}, {\"begin\": 2357, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999983290554473, \"rank\": 1.6452721951960851e-06, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both sporting\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2403}, {\"ngram\": \"financial ways\", \"from\": 2408, \"to\": 2422}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2483}, {\"ngram\": \"men's kitefoil\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He went on to rack up multiple titles, including back-to-back world championships, before winning bronze at Paris 2024, where kitefoiling made its debut.\",